*PreProd Jenkins Migration Is Postponed!*
---
There appear to be some strange interactions between plugins and configurations on the new PreProd Jenkins that are causing some rather intractable issues right now. Oddly the (nearly) identical configs and versions on Prod Jenkins work fine - so I think a security patch I included is perhaps the culprit.

That said, I'm not at all confident that I'll be able to get the new PreProd Jenkins instance to a good and stable spot (and resync'd, and revalidated) inside the next 90 minutes. :lolcry:

So! Have a lovely weekend, I'll get as much of this fixed up as I can this weekend, and we'll slate a new cutover date soon! (And hopefully you'll all forgive me for the 'hype train --> crashed train' ride I brought you on this week! :meow_this_is_fine: )
